Hi! My daughter has school assignment that require baking of focaccia with flower design on top. Just wondering.. do I need to punch down the dough after the first raise ?

This is possibly the easiest bread you can bake. 4 ingredients for the dough, no-knead. Prep this the night before!
.
Ingredients you’ll need: 
600g all-purpose flour 
480g water
7g of yeast 
3 tsp of salt 
Olive oil 
Some cloves of garlic
Couple sprigs of rosemary
.
Enjoy!

.
